quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,148,"Wọ́n gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. A sì fún wọn ní ìgbádùn títí di ìgbà díẹ̀."
  37,149,"Bi wọ́n léèrè wò pé: “Ṣé Olúwa rẹ l’ó ni àwọn ọmọbìnrin, tiwọn sì ni ọmọkùnrin?"
  37,150,"Tàbí A dá àwọn mọlāika ní obìnrin, tí àwọn sì jẹ́ ẹlẹ́rìí?”"
  43,37,"Dájúdájú àwọn èṣù náà yóò máa ṣẹ́rí wọn kúrò lójú ọ̀nà (ẹ̀sìn Allāhu). Wọn yó sì máa lérò pé dájúdájú àwọn ni olùmọ̀nà."
  43,38,"Títí di ìgbà tí ó fi máa wá bá Wa, ó sì máa wí pé: “Háà! Kí ó sì jẹ́ pé (ìtakété bí) ìtakété ibùyọ-òòrùn àti ibùwọ̀ rẹ̀ sì wà láààrin èmi àti ìwọ (èṣù alábàárìn yìí, ìbá dára); alábàárìn burúkú sì ni."
  43,39,"(Àbámọ̀ yín) kò níí ṣe yín ní àǹfààní ní Òní nígbà tí ẹ ti ṣàbòsí. (Àti pé) dájúdájú ẹ̀yin (àti òrìṣà yín) ni ẹ dìjọ máa kẹ́gbẹ́ nínú ìyà."
  44,22,"Nítorí náà, ó pe Olúwa rẹ̀ pé dájúdájú àwọn wọ̀nyí ni ìjọ ẹlẹ́sẹ̀."
  44,23,"(Allāhu sọ pé): “Mú àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi rìn ní alẹ́ (nítorí pé) wọn yóò tọ̀ yín lẹ́yìn."
  44,24,"Kí o sì fi agbami odò sílẹ̀ ní yíyanu sílẹ̀. Dájúdájú àwọn ni ọmọ ogun tí A máa tẹ̀rì sínú agbami."
  45,13,"Ó tún rọ ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀ pátápátá fún yín láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀. Dájúdájú àwọn àmì wà nínú ìyẹn fún ìjọ tó ní àròjinlẹ̀."
  45,14,"Sọ fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo pé kí wọ́n ṣàmójú kúrò fún àwọn tí kò retí àwọn ọjọ́ (tí) Allāhu (yóò ṣe àrànṣe fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo) nítorí kí Ó lè san ẹ̀san fún ìjọ kan nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  45,15,"Ẹníkẹ́ni tí ó bá ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, fún ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ ni. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì ṣe iṣẹ́ aburú, fún ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ ni. Lẹ́yìn náà, ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa yín ni wọn yóò da yín padà sí."
  46,1,"Hā mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)1 {1}",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah;  2:1.
  46,2,"Tírà náà sọ̀kalẹ̀ díẹ̀ díẹ̀ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu, Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n."
  46,3,"A kò ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀, àti ohunkóhun tó wà láààrin méjèèjì bí kò ṣe pẹ̀lú òdodo àti fún gbèdéke àkókò kan. Àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ yó sì máa gbúnrí kúrò níbi ohun tí A fi ṣèkìlọ̀ fún wọn."